rcov90.name: rcov90
rcov90.description: Semi-major axis radius (R) below which spaxels cover at least 90% of elliptical annuli with width R +/- 2.5 arcsec. This should be independent of the DAPTYPE.

snr_med_g.name: snr_med_g
snr_med_g.description: Median S/N per pixel in the ''griz'' bands within 1.0-1.5 R_{e}. This should be independent of the DAPTYPE. Measurements specifically for g.

snr_med_r.name: snr_med_r
snr_med_r.description: Median S/N per pixel in the ''griz'' bands within 1.0-1.5 R_{e}. This should be independent of the DAPTYPE. Measurements specifically for r.

snr_med_i.name: snr_med_i
snr_med_i.description: Median S/N per pixel in the ''griz'' bands within 1.0-1.5 R_{e}. This should be independent of the DAPTYPE. Measurements specifically for i.

snr_med_z.name: snr_med_z
snr_med_z.description: Median S/N per pixel in the ''griz'' bands within 1.0-1.5 R_{e}. This should be independent of the DAPTYPE. Measurements specifically for z.

snr_ring_g.name: snr_ring_g
snr_ring_g.description: S/N in the ''griz'' bands when binning all spaxels within 1.0-1.5 R_{e}. This should be independent of the DAPTYPE. Measurements specifically for g.

snr_ring_r.name: snr_ring_r
snr_ring_r.description: S/N in the ''griz'' bands when binning all spaxels within 1.0-1.5 R_{e}. This should be independent of the DAPTYPE. Measurements specifically for r.

snr_ring_i.name: snr_ring_i

snr_ring_z.name: snr_ring_z

sb_1re.name: sb_1re
sb_1re.description: Mean g-band surface brightness of valid spaxels within 1 R_e}. This should be independent of the DAPTYPE.

bin_rmax.name: bin_rmax
bin_rmax.description: Maximum g-band luminosity-weighted semi-major radius of any "valid" binned spectrum.

bin_r_n_05.name: bin_r_n_05

bin_r_snr_10.name: bin_r_snr_10
